@zpencer Could you review the Android app portion of this PR? It's essentially a clone of grpc-java's hello world app, with the gRPC bits swapped to C++ via JNI calls (oh, and a server added...)
Also, for consistency sake, if android allows it, I would suggest changing `grpc-helloworld.cpp` to `grpc-helloworld.cc`. All other C++ files in the repo use that extension
